Package mindless728.FluidFlow

Class Summary
BlockChanger Changes the blocks from the asynchronous threads that the fluids flow int
BlockData A place holder for the block data that each fluid may need
ChangedBlocks Keeps track of the list of changed blocks to keep order and a mapping from the blocks to the new changed types for fast access
Fluid the base fluid that is inherited by other plugin devs to create fluids
FluidBlock holds the data needed when a fluid is talking about a block
FluidBlockListener catches block based events
FluidFlow the main plugin that controls registration of fluid types
